text: Maulana Mohammad Mujahid Khan Al Hussaini was a Pakistani Islamic scholar and politician who served as Member of Provincial Assembly of the Khyber Pakhtunkhwa from 2002 to 2007. ==References== Category:1920 births Category:2014 deaths Category:Pashtun people Category:Darul Uloom Deoband alumni Category:Pakistani Islamic religious leaders Category:Pakistani Sunni Muslims Category:Jamiat Ulema-e-Islam politicians Category:People from Nowshera District Category:Pakistani Sunni Muslim scholars of Islam Category:North-West Frontier Province MPAs 2002–2007
title: Mohammad Mujahid Khan Al Hussaini
